data.description: Looking to have it all? Build a shop and stow your toys on well-placed generous gravel lot as part of this desirable Fruitland subdivision home. A move-in ready Contemporary, the distinctive layout features a well-designed, welcoming floor plan including 2 generous bedrooms and closets opposite primary bedroom/bath, walk-in closet, double sinks and lighted fog-free mirror.  Open concept living/dining/kitchen, leather finished granite counters, abundant storage, gas range and specialty lighting add custom distinction and function.  High end window treatments with ample natural light, a country view east-facing back patio and covered front porch for outdoor enjoyment.  Triple car garage with windowed doors. The backyard farm view parcel sits opposite a common area and walking path. Sellers report their favorite feature of the home as they have enjoyed it is the wonderful neighbors! All is ready for your personal touches.  Attractive price with generous seller incentives available. Who could ask for more!
